Tutti Frutti is a free new tab browser extension that can make your boring web experience more delightful. The background pops a tasty fruit basket to fulfill your cravings and next to it you can just click search. It’s like opening a new tab with a fresh background and our favorite search engine.

By clicking “Add to chrome”, I accept and agree to installing this new tab extension as well as its search settings, Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

The search features within the extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing.
